What it has *not* produced is a unified theory. The meta-variational principle remains a template. The Functorial Correspondence remains unproven. The connections between patterns are suggestive rather than deductive. The framework is best understood as a **research program** — a coordinated set of conjectures that may or may not cohere into a theory depending on what experiments reveal.

